               <msContents>
                  <summary>Emancipation of a slave.  The document is drawn up on behalf of two brothers who own a third part of a slave who, as regards the other two thirds had already been made free.  The ransom is paid by a private individual, perhaps the slave's prospective husband, rather than by the slave herself or by a banker</summary>
                  <msItemStruct>
                     <note type="general">Written along the fibers; on the back, part of a date</note>
                     <note type="general">42 lines; broken on right and with some damage to the left side</note>
                     <note type="general">The hand is a fluent cursive; signed by a slow writer</note>
